{"tid":2246734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「人民在捱餓邊緣」　台灣名嘴稱「大陸經濟大崩潰」惹議","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:53:54.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3b0829b84119b42943cf5233e61fc2c6cd10d6","tid":2246734,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201017/394073629224079360047963.png/R0Rwde4qqRx7bFRAOdk9Fk4zBw_ZSFRQp2cgsqdnILI?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201017%2F394073629224079360047963.png%2FR0Rwde4qqRx7bFRAOdk9Fk4zBw_ZSFRQp2cgsqdnILI%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=1c05487d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳經濟特區建立40周年之際，有台灣政論節目稱，大陸經濟大崩潰，廣州深圳街上都沒人，引起社會輿論關注。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》報道，在10月15日播出的一個台灣政論節目中，台灣媒體人吳國棟聲稱，大陸內部經濟已經大崩潰，並稱深圳龍華區馬路上「空空的」，這種情況已延伸到廣州。不僅如此，吳國棟還聲稱「大陸人民已經在面臨飢餓的邊緣」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/9d375b5c877be17c05dd06e5372a5ebe.png/BBVqa79iOnuJtQRzMt_z0eNt2D40V8fh3ffPs933z7M?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F9d375b5c877be17c05dd06e5372a5ebe.png%2FBBVqa79iOnuJtQRzMt_z0eNt2D40V8fh3ffPs933z7M%3Fv%3Dw640&h=8dd13b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息傳到大陸，不少網民留言表示，「這種愚昧宣傳，可憐井底之蛙。」還有網民留言稱，很難相信居然有很多人會盲目相信這些搞笑言論，揶揄這是「一本正經的自娛自樂」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/b4f6f7b7c8696099c7cbb8fe14efb644.png/xGT8rsMXyP4kmJlYpb_Ftbs7k-7VjG3cwp2Wl8Kdlpc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2Fb4f6f7b7c8696099c7cbb8fe14efb644.png%2FxGT8rsMXyP4kmJlYpb_Ftbs7k-7VjG3cwp2Wl8Kdlpc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5f3d269b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/9c146faa8d7b22f660760f1de23e1fe8.png/WSWp54mZHk-ScRPrFKdS6UTfjlGsVDxKFF06fhRdOn4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F9c146faa8d7b22f660760f1de23e1fe8.png%2FWSWp54mZHk-ScRPrFKdS6UTfjlGsVDxKFF06fhRdOn4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=14b46115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f99d1a2d34c66d598a45e92acd5ede5b4b2ff295","tid":2246734,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"大霸都冇事，你驚大陸冇野食？"},{"pid":"0207df943d720a61e4355f93448381e851dba184","tid":2246734,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣媒體人吳國棟聲稱，大陸內部經濟已經大崩潰，並稱深圳龍華區馬路上「空空的」，這種情況已延伸到廣州。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有睇YOUTUBE"},{"pid":"25738162839b8e6b9490090a5b05921cc88dc7bd","tid":2246734,"uid":148315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"中國首先要確保班黨員同兵有飯開<br />\n其次係班維穩嘅五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67f583998ac91116ae939e7fc78a78bd59e2959","tid":2246734,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"有十四億兩腳羊，點會冇嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88ca0921872ff7efc60ba50804b44b5da149baa","tid":2246734,"uid":282637,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVCfKsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVCfKsR.jpg&h=620c3f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"861a586df406c4c75e0f70b178490c9193aa5aa6","tid":2246734,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"食芯片<br />\n咩叫無嘢食"}]}